{
  "text": "Our algorithm is based on iteratively placing each node at the weighted centroid of its neighbors (simultaneously for all nodes). The aesthetic reasoning is clear; as explained in Section 5 this principle unifies the Tutte layout [CITATION_1] and the eigen-projection.",
